Tarnhem: The Balor who formally ruled the Layer called [[Noisome
Vale]], which is mentioned in the Manual of the Planes and originally
appeared in the Dungeon Builder's Guidebook by Bruce Cordell.
He also appeared in the 3.5 edition Tomb of Horrors conversion by Bruce R. Cordell. 
He is the father of, and an ally of, Acererak.
Sources: 
Manual of the Planes (3.0)
Dungeon Master's Guidebook
Return to the Tomb of Horrors
Tomb of Horrors (Revised)